###

### F) Assign roles (call only after there are 4 players)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/room/assign/c8f41b53-7d21-45ee-9ad5-0a9d7f50c4a4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### G) Get one player's role (replace <playerId>)
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/role/me/c8f41b53-7d21-45ee-9ad5-0a9d7f50c4a4/e22277a6-ac8f-4ab7-bce0-2823beb22e00

###

### H) Mantri submits guess (replace both ids)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/guess/c8f41b53-7d21-45ee-9ad5-0a9d7f50c4a4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mantriId": "e22277a6-ac8f-4ab7-bce0-2823beb22e00",
  "guessedPlayerId": "c1ae1167-91dd-4f23-92c4-47ce78964eb7"
}

###

### I) Get result
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/result/c8f41b53-7d21-45ee-9ad5-0a9d7f50c4a4

###

### J) Leaderboard
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/leaderboard/c8f41b53-7d21-45ee-9ad5-0a9d7f50c4a4

